{
  "R wrapper legend": {
    "prefix": "tox:legend_r",
    "body": [
    "!> @warning **IMPORTANT** - When using these R wrapper functions, copies of the arrays will be created.",
    "!| No direct modification of the original R objects occurs."
    ],
    "description": "Standard legend for R wrappers about array copy behavior"
  },
  "C wrapper legend": {
    "prefix": "tox:legend_c",
    "body": [
    "!> @warning **IMPORTANT** - When using these C wrapper functions, no copies of the arrays will be created.",
